Current builds of the greenlet package on one specific distro, are seeing an ICE on multiple architectures (ppc64le & riscv64) when being built with -fno-omit-frame-pointer.  The upstream github issue is here:

  https://github.com/python-greenlet/greenlet/issues/395

A minimized test case on Power is:

bergner@ltcden2-lp1:$ cat bug.c 
